-- Daiichi Sankyo, Kitasato Institute to Form Vaccines Venture, Nikkei Says
-- Fergus Maguire
-- 2010-07-25T21:31:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/daiichi-sankyo-to-form-joint-venture-to-make-flu-vaccines-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Daiichi Sankyo Co. will form a joint
venture with Kitasato Institute Research Center for Biologicals
to make vaccines as early as next spring, Nikkei English News
said, without citing anyone.   
 Daiichi Sankyo will take a majority stake in the new
company, which will focus on creating vaccines for a potential
flu epidemic, the report said.  
          
          


  


        